These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, handball, cycling, sailing
1. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is sailing##2
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Sport   | rowing | sailing | handball | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, goldfish, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the cat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Pet   | ferret | hedgehog | cat | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
